Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:23.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A love story between two police detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the detective boys are pulled in...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:26.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A surprising case rapidly develops!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body of a child and the brains of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:02.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:16.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, go ahead and get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:17.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did I do something wrong again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato san's birthday was in April and I went out with her for karaoke like I was supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She going to break up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W Wait, w wait. This is no joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fell for it! You fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:00.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll try it out on Yumi next
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, S-Sato san, are you saying you asked me here just to try it out on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:16.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were just heading home after work anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now look here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:25.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saying I shouldn't invite you somewhere except on business?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police Sergeant Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're in love, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The goal line might be getting near.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it please, Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it's an official request sent by the Tottori prefectural police?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know about it, don't you, Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About the gang of thieves centered in that-area that has been breaking into locations throughout the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye, talk to you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:13.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:17.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A joint investigation headquarters has been established in tottori...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they'd like someone from our Division one there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Superintendent, theft is Division Three's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten, Megure? They're guilty of attempted murder here in Tokyo too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course Division Three will be going, but we should send someone from Division One also.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whom should we assign?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They should be single, skillful, perceptive, and healthy enough to endure the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they should be familiar with the lay of the land around that area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm, oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Megure, isn't that guy's hometown somewhere near tottori?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Which guy are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:04.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? T Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a good choice, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite his appearance, he's a pretty sharp guy and I've heard he's solved a lot of difficult cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:25.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, Superintendent, I'll go ahead and contact him tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, let him know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure can be lonely to have to go somewhere far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hide's really going to a foreign country?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know if that's true yet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:44.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, England is where soccer originated, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're a fan, wouldn't you like to see him play at the original location?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you ask me, I think going overseas is a good thing if his goal is the World Cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The World Cup, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The World Cup... Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like the rain has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy's sure breathing heavily, like he's in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's only natural, since he's been jogging.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, we'd better hurry if we don't want to be late to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:31.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:32.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what they said. And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hear me, Miwako? Miwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh geez, I barely made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ohayou gozaimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh? Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm being sent to the Tottori joint investigation headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-They must have meant someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot! You're the only numskull named Takagi we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:46.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to what Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} said, Inspector Megure should already have contacted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Now that you mention it, the Inspector did phone me this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I was half asleep and didn't really understand what he was saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, see, it must have been that call.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, in any case. I'm sure I'll be back once the case has been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:13.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The headquarters has to investigate everything that gang of thieves has done throughout-the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:17.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely they will have to handle a huge number of cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's more, with so many criminals, even if you solve a case, how long do you think it will take?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, it'll be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the talents he will bring...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It will probably be all settled within three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three years?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-Three years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three years? 1095 days! 26780 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heaven hasn't abandoned me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great? The air is great in Tottori and you can eat all the Matsuba crab you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:51.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Note: Tottori prefecture, located in western Honshu, is famous for Matsuba crab (pacific snow crab in the US. queen crab in Europe)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you can ride a camel in the Tottori sand dunes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:55.38,Signs,,0,0,0,,Note: Tottori is also home to the Tottori Sand Dunes, the only large dune system in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not riding one of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, er, Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get me some 20th Century pears!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:07.81,Signs,,0,0,0,,Note: 20th century pears (nijiseki nashi) are considered the best tasting pears in Japan, initially cultivated at the beginning of the 20th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're my favorite food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're my favorite too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Matsuda crabs are my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take it easy during your absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's all the commotion about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The location is the 23rd floor of a high rise apartment building in Beika city's fourth district
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One man has been stabbed to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to this report, the body was discovered by a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato and Takagi, the both of you go to crime scene immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, as for the crime scene coordination, Megure, that's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, Superintendent
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about Chou san this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let Chou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} do it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:47.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please get going right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, this is the first time we've worked together, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm looking toward to it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah,yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is my senior by two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be sure to learn from the things he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, and also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This might be the last time he can team up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:34.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think Hide's press conference started at noon, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry, We'll miss seeing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, that conference will be today's top news item.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll probably be broadcast multiple times throughout the night
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Looks like something's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:50.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stabbing victim is Nakamoto Hirotoshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, 27 years old, an office worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder weapon was an all-purpose kitchen knife with an 18cm blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The presumed time of death was in the period between 7:00 and 7:30 AM today
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you're a coworker at his company who came here at 1PM and discovered him, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I took today off work in order to go with him to make the reservations for our marriage ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could something like this have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:21.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are there any people who disliked him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:28.54,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. H-He was the type that made enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like he was acquainted with the culprit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's no sign the lock was forced.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, could you pick out the people who you think hated him from an album for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We might find a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's Detective Takagi and Detective Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So then, please take care of that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a murder case, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah-Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It happened just after 7:00 this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We saw a suspicious person on the way to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was on a street near this apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person was just someone out jogging.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, it had stopped raining just before that man passed by, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it had been raining for about 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet, despite that, that man's clothes were just barely wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you think that was?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't he have just taken shelter somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must have started raining in the middle of his run.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:38.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when the rain stopped, he started his run again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, if he took a ten minute break, he wouldn't have been breathing so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:46.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, he wasn't breathing so hard because he's been jogging.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He may have been excited from killing someone in an indoor location somewhere nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what you wanted to say, right, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, was that man one of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, this person!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sort of looked like this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This person?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's one of our co workers, Katou san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he said he was staying at a friend's place though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:17.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know where it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sometime after 7:00 this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I've been here the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.32,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,In this apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Liar! It was you, wasn't it? The one who killed Hirotoshi'
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? I'm a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's all the noise about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's a door-to door salesman, just tell him to go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:44.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, what's it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, this makes it interesting, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? The suspect in a murder case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Katou here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder victim was a coworker at his company, Nakamoto Hirotoshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder weapon was a kitchen knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It had been dropped next to the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, when was the presumed time of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometime between 7:00 AM and 7:30 this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it was impossible for him to be the culprit then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because we were watching TV the whole time from when this guy woke me up at 7:00 until 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were watching the 7:00 live broadcast of the news-variety program "Morning Live 7" on Nichiuri TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, he woke you up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, couldn't he have recorded the program?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could have shown it to you afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have some good proof
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More importantly, how did you come to suspect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because you're my former boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:15:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are eyewitnesses who saw you near his apartment just after 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must have been half asleep that early in the morning and saw wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We weren't half asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it clearly, this person's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were wearing a gray parka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were running and carrying a black backpack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As if you wanted it to appear that you were jogging.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, let's have Detective Chiba show it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The proof that this man was watching TV from 7:00 to 8:00 this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is a complete mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I can see why you always oversleep and get in late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been trying real hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't I been late a lot less recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, you have, why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, I've been trying to improve myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with this mountain of toys?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be you're a tokusatsu geek?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:57.81,Signs,,0,0,0,,Note: Tokusatsu, literally special-fx, typically live-action movies and TV such as Godzilla. Ultraman, and countless sentai programs (like Power Rangers)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong with it? It's my hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gomera! It's Gomera!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a Kamen Yaiba too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a rare tin-plated one! handle them so roughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys! Didn't I tell you to wait in the patrol car with Katou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Shimura san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So where is it? whatever you were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thing that proves you two were watching TV together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. It's this video tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi! It's Okina Yoko's "Four Minute Cooking"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Friday, February the 25th.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tape this variety program, "Morning Live 7" everytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night I was drinking while watching a rental video with Katou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:44.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We fell asleep in here and I'd forgotten to set the automatic recorder, so I recorded it myself today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he couldn't have made a recording of the program beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we only use this one video deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's another deck here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only use that occasionally for dubbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:02.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he'd used this deck, I could see the cord in front of the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:05.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now matter how groggy I was, I think I would still have noticed it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you think I'm lying, please go ahead and inquire at the TV station for confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today is Friday, February the 25th.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nichiuri TV's "Morning Live 7" is the program just after the weather report
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, you've got a lot of others marked too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even cable TV programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of programs I might want to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's why there are so many memos stuck up around the TV screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then? After you watched until 8:00 like you said, what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We started watching a video after 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which video was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And adult video?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Kamen Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:27.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This has got to be episode one from the first series!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The original series looks a bit funny now, but this is still cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until what time were you watching this children's program?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Each tape is 120 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You watched this for two hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, using level three extended recording, not including the time for commercials...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You watched for six hours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:50.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Detective Chiba, did you record this video?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Katou recorded them a while ago and gave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And were you with him the entire time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:19:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, about halfway through watching, I took a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That took about 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we started watching once again, and when we stopped watching the video after 12 episodes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We started watching pro baseball directly thereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, it was the Falcons vs. Jaguars starting at 2:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we were in the middle of watching it when you and the others arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would take an hour and a half to get from here to the victim's apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they were together watching an hour of TV and afterwards almost six hours of video then he has an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just to be sure, will you let us search for the gray parka and black backpack the man was wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing important
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:01.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, if it's nothing, don't shout so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:06.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So? How long will you be sent to Tottori for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our seniors from Division One said it would be three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:12.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so? what did Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She asked me to bring her some 20th Century pears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's weird. Normally you'd expect her to be a little more upset
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, even if I get sent there, I guess I can take a vacation every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until last month he was overseas on business for a whole year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As soon as he got back, he called and asked if he could crash here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The girlfriend he lived with took up with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he had no place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And? And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though it seemed like he called her every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would just complain that he didn't understand women.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're serious, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you need to tell her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like what you're feeling, and what you intend to do in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's more, you don't know what will happen with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might just be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:11.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might find a girlfriend over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that happens, he might not be coming back for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:18.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:19.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say time and a people's hearts are inversely proportional. The more it passes, the more they grow apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's seems there are some rare exceptions though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am not going to get another girlfriend elsewhere! Definitely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "I"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:42.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were talking about Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:44.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might be going overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh right, Hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, as for Hide, I heard he decided to remain in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw the press conference this afternoon then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, just after "Morning Live 7" began they superimposed a quick news announcement
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Tokyo Spirits player, Akagi Hideo, indicated he will remain."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:05.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"There will be a press conference this afternoon staring at 12:00."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, did the newscaster say anything about that in the news afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:15.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it! That's what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's impossible. I still don't know how he performed this trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:27.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are still parts I can't explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:31.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did he do it? How did that guy create the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.08,0:24:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem there's anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.29,0:24:05.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At least not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.04,0:24:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for that, why don't you ask Detective Chiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.47,0:24:14.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba, will you swear on this Sakura badge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.93,0:24:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go over there and become a better detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.85,0:24:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, before I go, will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.23,0:24:24.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.49,0:24:36.16,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What-'s next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.20,0:24:36.78,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Two people!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:37.45,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.49,0:24:38.08,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,At last!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.12,0:24:38.66,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,A catastrophe?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.70,0:24:39.37,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Huh?
